item.title: Item Prices And Alchig prices
item.dc:creator: @Reamm28 Reamm28
item.description:
@Reamm28 wrote:

Go to your “Config” Folder first.
You will see a notepad named “Items”
Click on it and press “CTRL” “F”
Now put the item code there and it will find it
Scroll to the X Position (Right) and you will see more numbers
Replace the numbers to the numbers you want
